HAI 1.4
    VISIBLE "HOW MANY NUMBRZ?"
    I HAS A count
    GIMMEH count
    count IS NOW A NUMBR
    I HAS A total ITZ 0.0
    I HAS A i ITZ 0
    IM IN YR loop UPPIN YR i TIL BOTH SAEM i AN count
        VISIBLE "GIMME NUMBR " AN SUM OF i AN 1 AN ":"
        I HAS A num
        GIMMEH num
        num IS NOW A NUMBAR
        total R SUM OF total AN num
    IM OUTTA YR loop
    VISIBLE "TEH AVERAGE IZ " AN QUOSHUNT OF total AN count
KTHXBYE
